dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents buildings for Vilas County, Wisconsin in 2018.[The shape and orientation of the ground floor of all structures in a local government. This information is typically compiled from orthoimagery or other aerial photography sources. This representation of the building footprints support the local government basemaps.
